00:12:25.782 --> 00:12:27.034
and then
made her way here alone,

00:12:27.201 --> 00:12:28.579
all for Paul's sake,

00:12:28.746 --> 00:12:31.794
so she's got to be
a hell of a warrior.

00:12:31.961 --> 00:12:34.758
"With Roxy", that'd be nice.

00:12:36.219 --> 00:12:38.683
[RUDEUS] Damn, you two,
can't a guy eat in peace?

00:12:39.017 --> 00:12:40.687
