00:12:40.854 --> 00:12:43.442
but how does this woman keep
a harem of dudes around her

00:12:43.609 --> 00:12:45.029
and still avoid drama?

00:12:45.822 --> 00:12:48.786
I mean, as long as the fallout
doesn't hit me, whatever,

00:12:48.953 --> 00:12:49.997
but...

00:12:50.164 --> 00:12:51.124
[ELINALISE]
Here you are.

00:12:51.291 --> 00:12:53.003
The money I promised you.

00:12:53.546 --> 00:12:55.132
Thank you, my lady.

00:12:55.299 --> 00:12:56.761
You know, I feel kind of bad

00:12:56.927 --> 00:12:59.015
getting paid for something
that felt that good.

00:12:59.182 --> 00:13:00.560
Well, stop that.

00:13:00.727 --> 00:13:03.482
Just don't get serious about me,
and we're fine.

00:13:03.649 --> 00:13:07.991
[RUDEUS] Oh! So this is kind of
a reverse-prostitution thing.

00:13:08.534 --> 00:13:10.789
I guess that's okay. Right?

00:13:13.210 --> 00:13:18.178
[storm raging]

00:13:19.890 --> 00:13:21.685
[Rudeus grunting]

00:13:21.852 --> 00:13:23.689
-[knocking on door]
-[Rudeus exhales]

00:13:27.363 --> 00:13:29.785
Don't mind me,
just delivering your mail.

00:13:30.410 --> 00:13:31.956
Oh. Thank you.

00:13:33.083 --> 00:13:33.960
Hm.

00:13:36.381 --> 00:13:38.385
[RUDEUS]
"To Lord Rudeus Greyrat.

00:13:38.553 --> 00:13:40.515
I hope
this letter finds you well.

00:13:41.057 --> 00:13:42.769
I am Jinus, vice principal

00:13:42.936 --> 00:13:45.190
of the Ranoa University
of Magic".

00:13:46.067 --> 00:13:47.486
Wait a sec. Holy crap!

00:13:47.654 --> 00:13:49.282
That's Roxy's alma mater!

00:13:50.200 --> 00:13:52.539
"Word of your exploits
as 'Quagmire Rudeus'

00:13:52.706 --> 00:13:55.210
has reached us
here in the Kingdom of Ranoa.

00:13:55.377 --> 00:13:58.509
I understand you can cast spells
without incantations,

00:13:58.676 --> 00:14:00.053
and I've been informed

00:14:00.220 --> 00:14:02.141
that you also studied
under Roxy Migurdia,

00:14:02.308 --> 00:14:04.228
a King-class water mage."

00:14:04.813 --> 00:14:06.232
[ELINALISE]
"Should you have any desire

00:14:06.399 --> 00:14:08.821
to hone your magnificent craft
further still,

00:14:08.988 --> 00:14:11.409
Ranoa University of Magic
would be honored

00:14:11.577 --> 00:14:13.539
to welcome you
as a special student."

00:14:13.706 --> 00:14:15.334
Ooh. [giggles]

00:14:15.960 --> 00:14:17.212
Sounds important.

00:14:18.048 --> 00:14:19.551
[ELINALISE]
"Special students are exempt

00:14:19.718 --> 00:14:21.847
from both tuition
and regular class attendance,

00:14:22.014 --> 00:14:23.475
but retain full access

00:14:23.643 --> 00:14:25.772
to our on-campus libraries
and other facilities

00:14:25.939 --> 00:14:28.443
to conduct their own research
as they see fit."

00:14:28.945 --> 00:14:31.366
Wow. Sounds like a good deal.

00:14:34.706 --> 00:14:36.292
[RUDEUS]
"Would love to meet with you,

00:14:36.459 --> 00:14:38.881
thank you for your time
and consideration,

00:14:39.048 --> 00:14:41.762
signed God-Knows-Who
from God-Knows-Where".

00:14:42.262 --> 00:14:45.979
I am glad someone appreciates
my two years of hard work,

00:14:46.145 --> 00:14:48.149
and it's true that my magic's
kind of plateaued,

00:14:48.316 --> 00:14:50.237
so I am interested.

00:14:50.404 --> 00:14:53.744
But I need to verify
the authenticity of this thing.

00:14:57.292 --> 00:14:58.504
♪

00:14:58.671 --> 00:14:59.631
[WAITRESS 204A]
Thank you for waiting.

00:15:00.132 --> 00:15:02.261
Oh, that "special student"
program.

00:15:02.428 --> 00:15:03.304
Good stuff.

00:15:03.471 --> 00:15:05.100
So you do know it?

00:15:05.267 --> 00:15:07.479
Yeah, I thought I'd heard
that you attended school there.

00:15:07.647 --> 00:15:09.483
Can you tell me anything more
about it?

00:15:10.027 --> 00:15:11.404
[KONRAD]
Well, I didn't graduate,

00:15:11.572 --> 00:15:13.534
I dropped out in my fifth year.

00:15:13.701 --> 00:15:15.913
But yeah, the University
will sometimes reach out

00:15:16.080 --> 00:15:17.584
to people like you,

00:15:17.751 --> 00:15:19.420
who can cast weird spells
or have tons of mana,

00:15:19.588 --> 00:15:21.842
but aren't associated
with the Magician's Guild yet.

00:15:22.009 --> 00:15:23.637
Then, if they get famous later,

00:15:23.804 --> 00:15:25.474
that's good publicity
for the school.

00:15:27.186 --> 00:15:28.939
[RUDEUS]
Okay, I guess that tracks.

00:15:29.106 --> 00:15:30.860
I do cast weird spells.

00:15:31.027 --> 00:15:32.279
And if they do this a lot,

00:15:32.446 --> 00:15:34.450
then it's probably
not a total scam.

00:15:35.452 --> 00:15:36.830
Wait, so you're telling me,

00:15:36.997 --> 00:15:39.126
you've never been to school,
Quagmire?

00:15:39.628 --> 00:15:41.089
[RUDEUS]
I had a private tutor.

00:15:41.255 --> 00:15:44.220
Wow. Your family must've been
well-off, then.

00:15:44.386 --> 00:15:45.556
[RUDEUS]
Sort of.

00:15:45.723 --> 00:15:47.727
We have ties
to Asuran high nobility.

00:15:47.894 --> 00:15:49.271
[sighs] Right.

00:15:49.438 --> 00:15:51.735
Sorry, remind me
of your last name, again?

00:15:51.902 --> 00:15:54.115
[RUDEUS]
Greyrat, of the Notos Greyrats.

00:15:54.281 --> 00:15:57.121
Oh! Greyrat, huh?

00:15:57.287 --> 00:15:59.083
The liege lords of Asura?

00:15:59.835 --> 00:16:01.420
What're you doing
as a solo adventurer

00:16:01.588 --> 00:16:02.757
way out here, then?

00:16:02.924 --> 00:16:03.801
Hm?

00:16:04.719 --> 00:16:06.097
Well, my folks...

00:16:07.517 --> 00:16:09.855
-Oh, uh...
-I shouldn't have asked.

00:16:10.021 --> 00:16:12.652
But they went out of their way
to offer you a pretty good deal.

00:16:12.819 --> 00:16:15.658
You might as well go down there
and hear them out, at least.

00:16:15.825 --> 00:16:17.327
-You know?
-[RUDEUS] Yeah.

00:16:18.079 --> 00:16:19.624
And come to think of it,

00:16:19.791 --> 00:16:21.920
the only reason I went
to tutor Eris in the first place

00:16:22.087 --> 00:16:24.091
was so I could save up
tuition money.

00:16:24.968 --> 00:16:26.555
I'd totally forgotten.

00:16:26.722 --> 00:16:28.433
Attending the University
with Sylphiette

00:16:28.601 --> 00:16:29.853
was the original goal.

00:16:31.565 --> 00:16:33.652
I wonder what she's been up to
all this time.

00:16:34.905 --> 00:16:36.073
I hope she's all right.

00:16:36.240 --> 00:16:37.827
Ah! Oh!

00:16:37.994 --> 00:16:39.371
You should listen to him.

00:16:39.539 --> 00:16:41.250
School is a wonderful option,

00:16:41.417 --> 00:16:42.795
especially
when the only alternative

00:16:42.962 --> 00:16:44.758
would be rejoining Paul.

00:16:44.925 --> 00:16:46.427
[RUDEUS]
You think?

00:16:46.595 --> 00:16:49.099
I feel like reuniting my family
ought to come first.

00:16:49.266 --> 00:16:50.770
[ELINALISE] Paul is eventually
going to bring them all

00:16:50.937 --> 00:16:52.523
back to Asura anyway,

00:16:52.690 --> 00:16:54.151
just wait
'til they make it back safely

00:16:54.318 --> 00:16:55.696
and get settled in,

00:16:55.863 --> 00:16:57.825
and then take a shorter trip
to visit them.

00:16:57.992 --> 00:16:59.286
[RUDEUS]
You're saying that

00:16:59.453 --> 00:17:00.831
because you don't want
to see my father again,

00:17:00.998 --> 00:17:02.209
aren't you?

00:17:02.376 --> 00:17:03.879
-Guilty as charged.
-[KONRAD] Oh.

00:17:04.046 --> 00:17:06.175
[RUDEUS]
Whoa, she must really hate him.

00:17:07.135 --> 00:17:09.641
Well, improving my skills
is important.

00:17:10.267 --> 00:17:13.064
But attractive
as the University's proposal is,

00:17:13.231 --> 00:17:16.070
I don't think I can justify
taking them up on it right now.

00:17:30.516 --> 00:17:32.185
[RUDEUS]
Long time no see.

00:17:32.687 --> 00:17:34.023
[MAN-GOD]
Yup! Hi.

00:17:34.189 --> 00:17:36.193
[RUDEUS] What has it been,
two years now?

00:17:36.360 --> 00:17:38.907
I don't feel as nasty
as I did before.

00:17:39.074 --> 00:17:41.203
[MAN-GOD]
Aw, you missed me, huh?

00:17:41.705 --> 00:17:43.124
That's not what I said.

00:17:44.043 --> 00:17:45.504
Although, hey.

00:17:45.671 --> 00:17:47.090
I did try to reach out to you
a bunch of times

00:17:47.257 --> 00:17:49.053
while I was out
looking for Zenith.

00:17:49.219 --> 00:17:51.808
Would it have killed you
to show up for me even once?

00:17:51.975 --> 00:17:54.188
I had a lot going on my end.

00:17:54.355 --> 00:17:55.440
[RUDEUS]
Oh, yeah?

00:17:55.941 --> 00:17:58.404
Well, at least someone
eventually found her.

00:17:58.572 --> 00:18:01.118
Just feels like
I lost two whole years over it.

00:18:01.285 --> 00:18:02.496
Yeah, sorry.

00:18:02.663 --> 00:18:03.916
But I'm glad
you know where she is!

00:18:04.083 --> 00:18:05.628
[RUDEUS]
Thanks.

00:18:05.795 --> 00:18:07.882
I had no idea Roxy was out there
looking for her, too.

00:18:08.717 --> 00:18:11.097
[MAN-GOD] She's
a real go-getter, isn't she?

00:18:11.263 --> 00:18:12.975
[RUDEUS]
Yeah, you said it, but...

00:18:13.434 --> 00:18:15.773
I hope she gets back
from Begaritt sooner than later,

00:18:15.940 --> 00:18:17.359
I can't wait to see her.

00:18:17.902 --> 00:18:18.779
Oh, dear.

00:18:19.363 --> 00:18:20.658
Are you sure you want
your master

00:18:20.825 --> 00:18:22.411
to see how pathetic you are
right now?

00:18:22.578 --> 00:18:23.831
[grunts] Hey.

00:18:23.997 --> 00:18:25.166
I mean, think about it.

00:18:25.333 --> 00:18:26.962
Eris ran out on you,

00:18:27.129 --> 00:18:28.715
and when you finally had
a good thing going with Sara,

00:18:28.882 --> 00:18:30.970
your little guy
just wouldn't go to bat for you!

00:18:31.638 --> 00:18:33.684
Your spellcasting
may have improved a little,

00:18:33.851 --> 00:18:35.771
but you're really hitting a wall
lately.

00:18:35.938 --> 00:18:38.276
And your swordsmanship
hasn't gotten any better either!

00:18:38.443 --> 00:18:39.988
I know you practice every day,

00:18:40.155 --> 00:18:42.159
but boy, you don't have much
to show for it.

00:18:42.325 --> 00:18:43.662
Sure, you've built some muscle,

00:18:43.829 --> 00:18:45.415
but I don't think
you can stand before her

00:18:45.583 --> 00:18:47.002
and say with any confidence

00:18:47.169 --> 00:18:49.047
that you're a student
to be proud of, Rudy.

00:18:49.214 --> 00:18:51.595
Wow, you're really letting me
have it this time, huh?

00:18:51.762 --> 00:18:53.599
How about you get to the point
already?

00:18:54.851 --> 00:18:57.815
The point is that
you have a chance to shape up!

00:18:58.316 --> 00:19:00.654
Attend the University,
and I can promise you this:

00:19:00.821 --> 00:19:02.157
you'll learn so much more

00:19:02.324 --> 00:19:04.829
than a common adventurer
could ever hope to!

00:19:05.831 --> 00:19:08.754
What are you, every teacher
I had in high school?

00:19:08.921 --> 00:19:10.966
Oh, wait, you just kind of threw
that out there,

00:19:11.133 --> 00:19:13.847
but is that more
of your patented "Godly Advice"?

00:19:14.014 --> 00:19:16.310
[MAN-GOD]
Sure. You could say that. [hums]

00:19:16.477 --> 00:19:18.439
You do this thing where
literally everything you say

00:19:18.607 --> 00:19:20.778
-sounds suspicious and creepy.
-[MAN-GOD] Sorry!

00:19:20.945 --> 00:19:22.865
But you really should listen
this time.

00:19:23.032 --> 00:19:25.161
I'm giving it to you
as straight as I can.

00:19:25.328 --> 00:19:26.915
If you set out for Begaritt now,

00:19:27.082 --> 00:19:29.127
you will most assuredly
regret it.

00:19:29.921 --> 00:19:31.465
[RUDEUS]
Really. Why?

00:19:31.967 --> 00:19:33.177
Can't tell you!

00:19:33.344 --> 00:19:34.471
[RUDEUS]
Of course you can't.

00:19:34.639 --> 00:19:35.891
Well, this isn't the first time

00:19:36.058 --> 00:19:36.977
you've kept something important
from me,

00:19:37.143 --> 00:19:38.647
but you've got to realize

00:19:38.814 --> 00:19:40.483
that this whole interdimensional
man of mystery thing

00:19:40.651 --> 00:19:42.320
doesn't exactly make
a strong argument

00:19:42.487 --> 00:19:44.449
for whatever you're trying
to get me to do.

00:19:44.617 --> 00:19:46.120
I'd love
to take time for myself,

00:19:46.287 --> 00:19:48.917
but I'd much rather find
the rest of my family first.

00:19:49.084 --> 00:19:50.420
[MAN-GOD]
I see.

00:19:50.588 --> 00:19:52.465
Well, why don't I put it to you
another way?

00:19:52.633 --> 00:19:53.886
This ought to be good.

00:19:54.469 --> 00:19:55.681
[clears throat]

00:19:56.265 --> 00:19:57.602
Rudeus!

00:19:57.768 --> 00:20:00.273
Enroll in the Ranoa University
of Magic,

00:20:00.440 --> 00:20:02.612
and investigate
the Displacement Incident

00:20:02.778 --> 00:20:04.657
with their abundant resources!

00:20:04.824 --> 00:20:05.743
[gasps]

00:20:05.910 --> 00:20:07.370
If you do,

00:20:07.538 --> 00:20:10.376
You shall once again regain
your manly potency

00:20:10.544 --> 00:20:12.882
and, more importantly,
your pride!

00:20:13.049 --> 00:20:14.426
Oh! Really?

00:20:14.594 --> 00:20:16.388
Are you saying
that just by going to school,

00:20:16.556 --> 00:20:18.935
I can cure
my erectile dysfunction?

00:20:19.102 --> 00:20:21.148
-You are, right?
-[MAN-GOD] Your pride!

00:20:29.498 --> 00:20:34.007
[snoring]

00:20:34.174 --> 00:20:35.051
[RUDEUS]
Ah.

00:20:39.519 --> 00:20:42.482
[RUDEUS] Sure enough,
not a peep from the peen.

00:20:44.779 --> 00:20:47.409
-[Rudeus gasps]
-[Elinalise mumbling]

00:20:48.704 --> 00:20:51.876
[Elinalise snoring]

00:20:53.003 --> 00:20:57.345
Well, okay, if it'll get better.

00:20:59.726 --> 00:21:02.230
[bird chirping]

00:21:03.525 --> 00:21:06.113
-[wing flapping]
-[bird chirping]

00:21:11.123 --> 00:21:12.543
[RUDEUS]
Thank you for everything.

00:21:13.210 --> 00:21:14.254
Good luck, kid.

00:21:14.421 --> 00:21:15.799
Take care of yourself.

00:21:15.966 --> 00:21:16.843
[scoffs]

00:21:19.682 --> 00:21:22.353
[RUDEUS]
Sol, I really appreciate you.

00:21:22.521 --> 00:21:23.940
[SOLDAT]
Huh?

00:21:24.107 --> 00:21:25.401
I don't know how
I can ever repay all the things

00:21:25.569 --> 00:21:27.615
that you and your party
have done for me.

00:21:28.449 --> 00:21:29.952
[RUDEUS]
He may not want to admit it,

00:21:30.119 --> 00:21:31.581
but he's taken
really good care of me

00:21:31.748 --> 00:21:33.292
these last couple of years.

00:21:34.504 --> 00:21:36.048
In fact,
I've made pretty nice money

00:21:36.215 --> 00:21:37.300
exploiting your ass.

00:21:37.467 --> 00:21:38.762
So, thanks for that.

00:21:39.722 --> 00:21:41.810
Anyway, safe travels.

00:21:41.976 --> 00:21:43.145
Go get cured.

00:21:43.772 --> 00:21:45.316
[RUDEUS]
Yeah. I'll try.

00:21:45.483 --> 00:21:46.611
[SOLDAT]
Good.

00:21:46.778 --> 00:21:48.197
Well, I'm sure
we'll have business

00:21:48.364 --> 00:21:50.201
over in Ranoa one of these days.

00:21:50.368 --> 00:21:52.080
And when that happens,

00:21:52.247 --> 00:21:53.750
we ought to go
drinking and whoring again,

00:21:53.917 --> 00:21:55.461
just the two of us.

00:21:55.629 --> 00:21:56.506
Hm.

00:22:01.056 --> 00:22:03.227
[grunts and chuckles]

00:22:03.687 --> 00:22:04.939
[RUDEUS]
And so,

00:22:05.106 --> 00:22:07.277
